ssistance programs, with many food-based programs and\$\textbackslash{}backslash\$nscholarships being regressive. Governments should reconsider these programs \textendash{} or at least strengthen\$\textbackslash{}backslash\$ntheir design. They could look to the targeting mechanisms used by conditional cash transfers \textendash{} with\$\textbackslash{}backslash\$nimpressive rewards for progressivity},
